              &lt;xs:maxInclusive value="1"/&gt;
          &lt;/xs:restriction&gt;
      &lt;/xs:simpleType&gt;
  &lt;/xs:element&gt;
</pre>

The field shall be filled in with “1” if there is an agreement and
with “0” (zero) if there is not one.
